<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣١٥٢٤ - حَدَّثَنَا هُشَيْمٌ، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ الْحَكَمَ، وَحَمَّادًا،<span class="c5"> يَقُولَانِ:</span> <span class="c2">«هُوَ لِلِابْنِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>